actions.text: Referred to House Committee on House Administration.

official_title: A concurrent resolution providing for the printing of the First National Report of Project Baseline.

summary.text: Provides for the printing of a House document containing the First National Report of Project Baseline, a study of vocational education authorized by the Congress, and a summary. Provides that each Representative and Senator shall receive one copy, and that there shall be printed an additional two thousand copies, of which one thousand copies will be made available for the use of the House Committee on Education and Labor and one thousand for the use of the Senate Committee on Labor and Public Welfare.

titles.title: A concurrent resolution providing for the printing of the First National Report of Project Baseline.
